{"tid":32647,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港核電投資：大亞灣機組輕微滲漏液壓油　無洩漏輻射","createTime":"2016-12-10T09:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T04:23:16.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"34c282f25b1499da3f98cfb0ee6a17656fcf4dd1","tid":32647,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:46:52.000Z","msg":"港核電：大亞灣機組輕微滲漏液壓油　無洩漏輻射<br />\n2016-12-10 HKT 16:40<br />\n<br />\n內地微信公號「中國核能」昨日透露，深圳大亞灣核電站上月發生主泵阻尼器洩漏事件，有關訊息其後被刪除。香港核電投資有限公司表示，核電站的 1 號機組大修期間沒有洩漏任何輻射。<br />\n<br />\n港核電下午發聲明澄清，指大亞灣核電站 1 號機組上月16日按計畫停機檢修，期間工作人員發現一個阻尼器輕微滲漏液壓油，已派人維修並恢復運作。<br />\n<br />\n核電公司補充，阻尼器於地震發生時會利用液壓油作緩衝之用，兩者均沒有放射性，不會對員工、核電站及環境造成影響，不屬於運行事件。"},{"pid":"d424942c0765fa0afbc7881313e6431ae1e8deaf","tid":32647,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:51:23.000Z","msg":"新界rip"},{"pid":"6ee3e266ba9a88203c55089205fb2482326ae463","tid":32647,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:54:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4b77ebbf1c3567574cf3c7b464d2836695963a5","tid":32647,"uid":33808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T10:12:07.000Z","msg":"根本係武器來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065d55b8f9032f5e7ce5efc6c611a7edb0bab55d","tid":32647,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T10:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有漏你都唔會認架啦"},{"pid":"5549880a1deffc1e3d2fe15d0abd4f9216ce53a2","tid":32647,"uid":33970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T10:27:01.000Z","msg":"搵人裝個輻射探測儀去塔門mon住<br />\n一超標就知漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e03f2913ef6cbe367c2a22d435eae1e704f68c","tid":32647,"uid":29928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T10:27:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquo